{"tid":1990062,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港警聯絡柏克萊分校招聘留學生　學生組織促校方拒絕　免損校譽","createTime":"2020-04-26T11:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T12:28:49.000Z","uid":5195,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aa9df7b778fad362f245189445b0da90d74530d8","tid":1990062,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T11:58:48.000Z","msg":"截至 2 月，今年度投考警員和督察的人數分別比上年度下跌約三成半及四成。加州大學柏克萊分校香港事務組（HKAAB）在專頁發文指，近日得知香港警隊接觸柏克萊加州大學（UC Berkeley）的事業策劃中心，希望招募該校的香港學生。HKAAB表示，已建議事業策劃中心回絕警隊的招募邀請。組織亦已拒絕參與警隊招募的宣傳工作，稱相信學生都不會損害校譽。<br />\n<br />\n立場詳盡報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E6%9F%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%90%8A%E5%88%86%E6%A0%A1%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E7%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E4%BF%83%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95-%E5%85%8D%E6%90%8D%E6%A0%A1%E8%AD%BD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E6%259F%258F%25E5%2585%258B%25E8%2590%258A%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%2581%2598%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595-%25E5%2585%258D%25E6%2590%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E8%25AD%25BD%2F&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4IWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=9aeb22ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E6%259F%258F%25E5%2585%258B%25E8%2590%258A%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%2581%2598%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595-%25E5%2585%258D%25E6%2590%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E8%25AD%25BD%2F&h=ea9a0687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h